<body>
Reports situations when a number of parameters in VALUES does not match a number of columns
  in a target table.
<p>Example (MySQL):</p>
<pre><code>CREATE TABLE foo(a INT, b INT, c INT);

INSERT INTO foo VALUES (1,2,3,4)</code></pre>
<p>The <code>foo</code> table has three columns but in the INSERT INTO statement we pass four.</p>
